{"tid":1050483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【華為大反擊】宣佈控告美國政府 禁聯邦機構買華為產品違憲","createTime":"2019-03-07T02:29:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T04:21:35.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5ec7c35898f6a707a0e944dbc1bfb33465d5b272","tid":1050483,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190307/large/1551925295_00f3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190307%2Flarge%2F1551925295_00f3.png&h=7f26faac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國電訊設備製造商華為今早宣佈，已入稟美國德州地區法院控告美國政府，指控他們禁止聯邦機構使用華為的產品，有關行為涉嫌違反美國憲法。<br />\n<br />\n華為在有關聲明中指，美國國會通過《國防授權法》，卻一直未能提供對華為涉嫌竊密指控的實際證據，也沒有給予華為辯護的機會，因此華為要以法律手段維護權益。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，德州是華為美國總部所在地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190307/59339306\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190307%2F59339306&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QD11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=50908046\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190307%2F59339306&h=cc0ec173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190307/59339306</a>"},{"pid":"172cabb66967417fd4936dd1ad25e53d351d77a0","tid":1050483,"uid":188155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:29:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3dd555b7151d263df1b192c6665cce081a46db4f","tid":1050483,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:16:24.000Z","msg":"若現屬實,feel到華為有機會贏<br />\n始終美國法律唔睇你邊位"},{"pid":"d95a4901a1e6ca279abfbc40dadbfbbe9e053d44","tid":1050483,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:17:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>若<span style=\"color: red;\">言</span>屬實,feel到華為有機會贏<br 